        {
            "id": "https://blog.mengcodes.com/Notes/2021/02/22/2/",
            "url": "https://blog.mengcodes.com/Notes/2021/02/22/2/",
            "title": "Nvm安装及日常使用",
            "date_published": "2021-02-22T07:58:50.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>node.js 的版本管理工具 Nvm 的安装及日常使用<br />\n<a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>项目中经常遇到不同项目需要不同的 <span class=\"red\">node.js</span> 版本或者你本地 node 版本与客户现有系统的 <span class=\"red\">node.js</span> 版本相差较大等情况，我们肯定不可能卸载现有的再装客户需要的，这时 <span class=\"red\">Nvm</span> 就派上了用场。通过 <span class=\"red\">Nvm</span>，我们可以来回切换不同版本的<span class=\"red\"> node.js</span>，十分方便。</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"nvm的安装\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#nvm的安装\">#</a> Nvm 的安装</h1>\n<h2 id=\"mac安装\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#mac安装\">#</a> mac 安装</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL252bS1zaC9udm0vYmxvYi9tYXN0ZXIvUkVBRE1FLm1k\">官方 md:https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm/blob/master/README.md</span> (多打开几次，比较慢)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight js\"><figcaption><span>安装</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 命令行代码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">curl -o- https:<span class=\"comment\">//raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.37.2/install.sh | bash</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 或者</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">wget -qO- https:<span class=\"comment\">//raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.37.2/install.sh | bash</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>安装完成后关闭终端，重新打开终端输入 <span class=\"red\">nvm</span> 验证一下是否安装成功，当出现 <span class=\"red\">Node Version Manager</span> 时，说明已安装成功。如下图：（单击可放大）<br />\n<img data-src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/02/22/JFC4bwHGuinTs2X.jpg\" alt=\"1613984786965.jpg\" /></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"windows安装\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#windows安装\">#</a> windows 安装</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>下载<span class=\"blue\"> nvm-windows</span> <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2NvcmV5YnV0bGVyL252bS13aW5kb3dz\">https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows</span> (多打开几次，比较慢)</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"nvm的简单使用\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#nvm的简单使用\">#</a> Nvm 的简单使用</h1>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight js\"><figcaption><span>简单使用</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 简单使用</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nvm list  <span class=\"comment\">// 查看已安装所有node版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nvm install <span class=\"number\">10.15</span><span class=\"number\">.0</span> <span class=\"comment\">// 安装指定版本node</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nvm uninstall <span class=\"number\">10.15</span><span class=\"number\">.0</span> <span class=\"comment\">//卸载指定版本的node</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nvm use <span class=\"number\">10.15</span><span class=\"number\">.0</span> <span class=\"comment\">// 切换node版本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nvm alias <span class=\"keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"number\">10.15</span><span class=\"number\">.0</span> <span class=\"comment\">// 指定默认版本号</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"blue\">nvm list</span><br />\n<img data-src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/02/22/uZTEmztkdjBQneP.jpg\" alt=\"list.jpg\" /></li>\n<li><span class=\"blue\">nvm use [version]</span><br />\n<img data-src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/02/22/KdJIkEB9LfWpT5X.jpg\" alt=\"use.jpg\" /></li>\n<li><span class=\"blue\">nvm install [version]</span><br />\n<img data-src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/02/22/EX3NHCxZ7lFT4dg.jpg\" alt=\"install.jpg\" /></li>\n<li><span class=\"blue\">nvm uninstall [version]</span> (不能卸载正在使用的版本，会报 nvm: Cannot uninstall currently-active node version, v6.17.1 (inferred from 6.17.1).)<br />\n<img data-src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/02/22/oPNZk9ywujIS2le.jpg\" alt=\"uninstall.jpg\" /></li>\n<li><span class=\"blue\">nvm alias default [version]</span><br />\n<img data-src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/02/22/zcnAdFDIk2ZpamN.jpg\" alt=\"default.jpg\" /></li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>日常这几个命令已经够用了。<br />\n<span class=\"label danger\">❤️筱何仔</span></p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "笔记"
            ]
        },
